Name: Book
Description: A well known novel written by a very renowned writer... not sure who could it be.
es_Description: Una novela muy conocida escrita por un autor muy aclamado por la critica... no se quien sea.

Name: Bookshelf
Description: A wooden board and a couple of nails of dubious quality. I wouldn't place a whole book saga on it.
es_Description: Una tabla y un par de clavos de dudosa calidad. No pondria una saga completa de libros sobre ella.

Name: Camera
Description: With the almost latest technology, this camera can be place anywhere inside (not suitable for exteriors)
es_Description: Con tecnologia de anteultima, esta camara puede colocarse en cualquier interior (No apta para exteriores).

Name: Chair
Description: At the store you've found the most comfy chair in the world. With unique materials. It was way too expensive.
es_Description: En la tienda viste la silla mas comoda que jamas existio. Con materiales unicos. Era cara y compraste esta.

Name: Chess Board
Description: A perfect board to play chess. Or checkers. Or curling... it is true, google it.
es_Description: Un tablero perfecto para jugar al ajedrez. O a las damas. O al curling... es verdad, googlealo.

Name: ChoppingBoard
Description: The board was in discount because the previous owner chopped his finger off with it. It's still bloody.
es_Description: La tabla estaba en descuento porque el anterior dueno se rebano el dedo con ella. Aun tiene sangre.

Name: Coconut
Description: If we delete it from the game, it won't compile.
es_Description: Si lo borramos del juego, no compila.

Name: Strange Cube
Description: In the event that the strange Cube does speak, F.a.r team urges you to disregard its advice.
es_Description: En el caso de que el Cubo Raro hable, F.a.r team te insta a ignorar su consejo.

Name: Computer
Description: A computer that has KTA preinstalled.
es_Description: Una computadora que viene con KTA preinstalado.

Name: Console
Description: A cubic console with a huge green X and the first CD reader in history.
es_Description: Una consola de juegos con forma cubica, una equis verde enorme y el primer lector de CDs de la historia.

Name: Counter
Description: This outlined square seems to be a counter. Such disastrous artists.
es_Description: Este cuadrado delineado parece ser una encimera. Que artistas nefastos.

Name: Desk
Description: 8 out of 10 people misplaces this desk.
es_Description: 8 de cada 10 personas colocan mal este escritorio.

Name: Dishes
Description: Stacking dishes in pixel art is very complicated, do not complain.
es_Description: Apilar platos en pixel art es muy complicado, no se quejen.

Name: Dumbbells
Description: Tired of never having them available at the gym, you bought this set. Someone's using it.
es_Description: Harto de que nunca esten disponibles en el gimnasio, compraste este set. Alguien lo esta usando.

Name: Fridge
Description: Inside there are two bee eggs, an expired milk carton and a vegetable you don't remember buying.
es_Description: Adentro hay dos huevos de abeja, un carton de leche vencida y una verdura que no recuerdas haber comprado.

Name: Outlet Kit
Description: Use it to electrify objects.
es_Description: Sirve para electrificar objetos.

Name: Pipeline Kit
Description: Use it to connect objects to the water supply.
es_Description: Sirve para conectar objetos a la red de agua.

Name: Lamp
Description: The place is integrated with bioluminescence, which renders this lamp useless. But it is cute.
es_Description: El lugar ya viene con bioluminiscencia integrada, lo que vuelve inútil a esta lampara. Pero es bonita.

Name: Microwave
Description: mmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm BEEP BEEP BEEP BEEP
es_Description: mmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm BEEP BEEP BEEP BEEP

Name: Mug
Description: It clearly reads "Football superstar". You've never touched a ball in your life.
es_Description: Claramente se lee "Futbolista numero 1". Nunca tocaste una pelota en tu vida.

Name: Oven
Description: This magical oven does not require a gas system, since it feeds on people's misfortune.
es_Description: Este horno magico no requiere de un sistema de gas, puesto que se alimenta de la desdicha de la gente.

Name: Pan
Description: A long-haired princess was selling this as a "self-defense weapon". Her chameleon looked at you ugly.
es_Description: Una princesa de pelo largo vendía esto como un "arma de defensa personal". Su camaleon te miraba feo.

Name: Pizza Box
Description: It has a note. "Well I didn't win, here's your pizza". The box is empty.
es_Description: Tiene una nota. "No gane, aqui esta la pizza". Está vacía.

Name: Plant
Description: A very easy plant to care for. It needs sun from 4 to 5, otherwise it will growl. The list keeps going.
es_Description: Una planta muy sencilla de cuidar. Necesita sol de 4 a 5, sino grita. Solo bebe agua filtrada, sino grita.

Name: Raygun
Description: A perfect weapon to destroy the front door and escape this nightmare. It came without batteries.
es_Description: Un arma prefecta para destruir la puerta de entrada y escapar de esta pesadilla. Vino sin pilas.

Name: Scale
Description: It doesn't dial numbers, just very offensive jokes about your weight and... financial position?
es_Description: No marca numeros, solo chistes muy ofensivos sobre tu peso y tu... posicion economica?

Name: S. Couch
Description: The S is for Small. Perfect if nobody loves you.
es_Description: La I es por individual. Perfecto por si nadie te quiere.

Name: Sink
Description: The water looks drinkable, but considering it's 1980, it's probably laced with mercury.
es_Description: El agua se ve potable, pero considerando que estamos en 1980, probablemente esta inundada en mercurio.

Name: TeaSet
Description: It comes with all kinds of teas: black, strawberry... that's it.
es_Description: Viene con tes de todos los sabores: negro, fresa... eso es todo.

Name: Test Tubes
Description: They have labels. "Sugar", "Spice", "Everything Nice"... The one labeled "Chemical X" is empty.
es_Description: Tienen etiquetas. "Azucar", "Flores", "Muchos Colores"... El que dice "Sustancia X" está vacio.

Name: Toaster
Description: I don't think it is a good idea to put a knife into it.
es_Description: No creo que sea buena idea meterle un cutucuchillo.

Name: Toilette
Description: It's an old toilet from a public restroom, plated in gold. The paint is peeling in places.
es_Description: Es un antiguo inodoro de un bano publico banado en oro. La pintura se cae en algunas partes.

Name: Wash Mach.
Description: With its off-centered engine, it's the number one enemy of the downstairs neighbors. Luckily, this is a house.
es_Description: Con su motor descentrado, es el enemigo numero uno de los vecinos de abajo. Por suerte esto es una casa.

Name: Alien
Description: They were on sale online. They're very common these days.
es_Description: Estaban en descuento en internet. Son muy comunes en esta epoca.

Name: Bathtub
Description: It washes, scrubs, and deducts taxes. With one use, you'll be completely clean.
es_Description: Lava, frota y deduce impuestos. Con un uso vas a estar completamente limpio.

Name: Staycycle
Description: A bicycle that stays still.
es_Description: Una bicicleta que se queda quieta.

Name: Cabinet
Description: How do you draw a top view cabinet?
es_Description: como se dibuja un gabinete desde arriba?

Name: Clone
Description: It looks like you, but you are more handsome.
es_Description: Luce como tu... pero tu eres mas guapo.

Name: Couch
Description: The cornerstone of every home and of this game.
es_Description: La piedra angular de todo hogar y de este juego.

Name: DinnerTable
Description: The wood is so high quality that it self-destructs when dirty, so you don't waste time cleaning.
es_Description: La madera es de tan buena calidad que se autodestruye al ensuciarse, para que no pierdas tiempo limpiando.

Name: DumbbellRack
Description: This dumbbell set ranks from 200g to 4T.
es_Description: Este set de pesas va desde 200g a 4T.

Name: Island
Description: It's like a countertop but better, because bigger is always better.
es_Description: Es como una encimera pero mejor, porque mas grande siempre es mejor.

Name: Bed
Description: Apparently, the way it looks makes you want to smell it. Please don't.
es_Description: Al parecer, te dan ganas de olerla por como luce. Por favor, no lo hagas.

Name: Race Track
Description: Brooooooooooom
es_Description: Fiuuuuuuuuuuuuuuum

Name: Sarcophagus
Description: After a raid on one of the biggest criminals, the English museum, they began selling them.
es_Description: Luego de un allanamiento a uno de los criminales más grandes, el museo inglés, comenzaron a venderlos.

Name: Sword
Description: Incredibly sharp, like a bowling ball.
es_Description: Increiblemente afilado, como una bola de boliche.

Name: TvTable
Description: The drawers are full of the previous owner's junk. Nothing of value.
es_Description: Los cajones estan llenos de basura del anterior dueno. Nada de valor.

Name: Treadmill
Description: How are you going to walk in... ah... *disconnects from Discord* (Description suggested by a programmer)
es_Description: Como vas a caminar en... ah... *se desconecta de Discord* (Descripcion sugerida por un programador)

Name: Tv
Description: Two hundred channels and nothing but cats.
es_Description: Doscientos canales y solo veo gatos.

Name: Bar
Description: It's just an island with benches, nothing unusual.
es_Description: Es solo una isla con banquitos, nada raro.

Name: Big Bed
Description: Do. Not. Smell. It.
es_Description: No. La. Huelas.

Name: Big Table
Description: I don't understand why you bought a family-sized table if no one loves you...
es_Description: No termino de entender por que compraste una mesa tamano familiar si nadie te quiere...

Description: CONFIRMED!
es_Description: CONFIRMADO!

Name: Piano
Description: Did you know that the creators of Piano Tiles 2 are following one of our developers on Twitter?
es_Description: Sabias que los creadores de piano tiles 2 siguen a uno de nuestros desarrolladores en twitter?

Name: RoundTable
Description: It's the big table. You can see the saw marks on the corners.
es_Description: Es la mesa grande. Se notan las marcas de sierra en las esquinas.

Name: WeightBench
Description: It comes with a coupon for a shady cryptocurrency online course.
es_Description: Viene con un cupon para un curso turbio de criptomonedas.

Name: CCTV Monitor
Description: It can monitor up to nine different cameras and comes with minesweeper.
es_Description: Puede monitorear hasta nueve camaras distintas y viene con el buscaminas.

Name: Labeler
Description: Use it to change a room's label.
es_Description: Usalo para cambiar la etiqueta de una habitacion.

Name: Sledgehammer
Description: Use it to unlock a room without paying.
es_Description: Sirve para desbloquear una habitacion sin gastar dinero
